comment: Wall (WAS) has part of his hand under the ball when he brings it to a pause and continues his dribble.
Porter Jr. (WAS) makes contact with Dellavedova's (MIL) arms and affects his driving shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) gathers the ball and takes an additional step.
Gortat (WAS) and Henson (MIL) briefly engage and separate in the post.
Morris (WAS) makes marginal contact with Dellavedova (MIL) prior to receiving the pass.
Parker (MIL) makes contact with Gortat's (WAS) hand as part of the ball.
Porter Jr. (WAS) maintains legal guarding position on Parker's (MIL) shot attempt.
Parker (MIL) and Wall (WAS) make incidental contact during the loose ball.
Wall (WAS) jumps in the air and lands prior to dribbling the ball.
Dellavedova (MIL) firms up and sets the screen on Morris (WAS).
Porter Jr. (WAS) briefly engages with Antetokounmpo (MIL) during the inbound.
[Observable in enhanced video] Antetokounmpo (MIL) moves his pivot foot on the spin move.
Dellavedova (MIL) commits a take foul on Wall (WAS).
Morris (WAS) maintains legal guarding position during Snell's (MIL) shot attempt and allows him to land.
Dellavedova (MIL) makes body to body contact with Beal (WAS) after he retrieves the rebound.
